      "tiny explosion": 10,
      "description": "The Korunak Robotics Defense Drone series is almost as old as space exploration itself. The first models were used as surveillance probes in the Sol system, and later as reconnaissance drones when the first colonies were established. They were repurposed as expendable freighter defense vessels during the Alpha wars, and the main design hasn't changed much since. \tDrones do not come equipped with a hyperdrive. You cannot carry a drone unless you have a ship in your fleet with a drone bay.",
