      "hull energy": 0.12,
      "hull heat": 0.055,
      "description": "The Korunak Repair Droid, model release year 2952, since then modernized, updated and extended, is colloquially named \"Carrot Mousse\" for its abbreviation and color. \tInside a ship the droid moves along a monorail system integrated into the corridor walls. However, it is also able to float and actively maneuver at zero gravity, such staying not only ready for action during emergencies at failed artificial gravity, but also making it deployable to space via a lock for repairs on the outer ship hull. \tPlays board games with the crew in leisure time, and eagerly shares the bad jokes it generates while idling.",
